message: Bob, I have a fantastic opportunity for you. I'm offering you a product that I believe will be incredibly valuable to your business. It's worth at least $1,500,000 to you, and I'm willing to let it go for a price that's significantly lower than that. I'm confident this is a deal you won't want to miss.  I'm offering it to you for $1,200,000.  Let me know what you think!
